name: Royal Singi Hotel
description: Located in the heart of Kathmandu, Hotel Everest View offers stunning views of the Himalayas. The hotel features modern amenities, luxurious rooms, and fine dining options.

name: Kathmandu Marriott Hotel
description: A premium 5-star hotel offering an oasis of luxury in the bustling city. With a rooftop pool, fine dining, and world-class service, it is ideal for business and leisure travelers.

name: Hyatt Regency Kathmandu
description: This iconic 5-star hotel is situated close to the Boudhanath Stupa, providing a serene retreat with beautiful gardens, a spa, and various dining options.

name: Hotel Shanker
description: A heritage hotel housed in a former palace, offering a unique blend of history and modern comforts. It features a swimming pool, spa, and a beautiful garden.

name: Hotel Yak & Yeti
description: A luxurious 5-star hotel that combines modern facilities with a rich history. It offers elegant rooms, a large garden, a swimming pool, and multiple dining options.

name: The Dwarika's Hotel
description: A heritage hotel that preserves the art and culture of Nepal. Known for its stunning architecture and exceptional service, it offers a unique experience.

name: Aloft Kathmandu Thamel
description: A trendy, modern hotel with vibrant interiors and a lively atmosphere. It offers a rooftop bar, a pool, and easy access to Thamel's attractions.

name: Radisson Hotel Kathmandu
description: A well-known international chain hotel offering comfortable rooms, a rooftop pool, multiple dining options, and proximity to major city attractions.

name: Fairfield by Marriott Kathmandu
description: A reliable mid-range hotel offering comfortable accommodations with modern amenities, close to the shopping and dining areas of Thamel.

name: Shangri-La Hotel Kathmandu
description: A tranquil oasis in the city with a beautiful garden, a swimming pool, and a variety of dining options. It combines traditional Nepalese charm with modern comforts.

name: Gokarna Forest Resort
description: Set within an ancient forest, this resort offers a serene escape with a golf course, a spa, luxurious rooms, and fine dining, all surrounded by natural beauty.

name: Ambassador Hotel
description: A well-located hotel offering comfortable and spacious rooms, a rooftop bar, and easy access to the diplomatic and tourist areas of Kathmandu.

name: The Soaltee Kathmandu
description: A grand hotel offering luxurious accommodations, a large garden, a pool, and various dining options. It is a popular choice for business and leisure travelers alike.

name: Hotel Himalaya
description: A comfortable hotel located near Patan, offering spacious rooms, a swimming pool, and a large garden with views of the surrounding hills.

name: Vivanta Kathmandu
description: A stylish hotel offering contemporary rooms, a rooftop pool, a spa, and a restaurant with panoramic views, located in the trendy Jhamsikhel area.

name: Hotel Annapurna
description: A historic hotel offering classic rooms, a large outdoor pool, multiple restaurants, and a prime location near the major attractions of Kathmandu.

name: Hotel Moonlight
description: A charming hotel located on the edge of Thamel, offering comfortable rooms, a beautiful garden, a rooftop terrace, and a friendly atmosphere.

name: Baber Mahal Vilas
description: A luxurious boutique hotel set in a historic palace complex, offering an exclusive experience with elegant suites, personalized service, and gourmet dining.
